                        h4 SECTOR - Rapid roll-up, full curtain and counterweights



                        p(class='lead') A fully featured and practical solution.When handling vehicles require frequent crossings, heavy duty, compact size rapid doors are required.


                        p(class='lead') Sector rapid roll-up doors not only meet these requirements, but also feature a fully coated frame housing the motor, the control and safety devices and the balancing systems.


                        p(class='lead') In addition to being good value for money, Sector doors also boast a high level of flexibility, ensured by the structure and by the availability of several designs.







                        h4(class='h5')  Technical features of the product range





                        ul(class='dot-before') 
                            li Compact hot galvanised steel or fine satin finish AISI 304 stainless steel structure

                            li Reduced size structure, specially in height

                            li The self supporting casing, fitted on suitable vertical uprights, makes door installation easy and houses and protects all moving parts

                            li The optional automatic antipanic device allows, in the event of a power cut, the curtain to be reopened by using the counterweights

                            li Reliable modular counterweighted balancing system

                            li IP55 rated electronic panel complete with pushbutton panel with open-close-stop membrane control featuring anautotest function, compliant with European Directives 2006/42/EC and 89/106/EC. TÜV certified

                            li Emergency release system

                            li Polarised quick wiring

                            li 3-phase motor for heavy duty operation and different speeds, accelerations and braking control system

                            li Complete range of bottom edges to be connected to the curtain by means of a special extruded anodised aluminium universal profile complete with ACS side runners – Anti crash System: passive edge, electromechanical sensitive edge and SOF self testing safety rib.





